      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so excited to show you this car\u2014it is a total gem! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it that it still looks and feels like it just left the dealership. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, always kept clean and running perfectly. If you're looking for something that\u2019s basically brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one! You\u2019ve really gotta see it in person to see how much it shines. Drop me a message if you want to come by and take a look!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E46 M3 in concours condition. This chassis is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and a 8,000 RPM redline. The VANOS system has been completely overhauled with Beisan components, and rod bearings were replaced as preventative maintenance. Power is managed through a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock. The subframe has been professionally reinforced to ensure structural integrity. The suspension features fresh OEM bushings and dampers, maintaining factory-spec kinematics. Finished in Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather, the paint depth is consistent across all panels with zero orange peel or swirl marks. This is a mechanically transparent, turn-key example for the technical purist.",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Flawless exterior. Original paint. Interior like new. Mechanical inspection passed. Garage kept. No accidents.",
      "price": 44000.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, having been meticulously garaged and cared for since day one. The exterior finish retains its deep, factory luster with zero swirls or stone chips, protected by a professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather seats show no signs of wear, and the original protective films remain on several interior accents. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service log from the dealership and all scheduled maintenance performed ahead of time. It drives tight, quiet, and powerful, just as it did on the showroom floor. Includes all original manuals, both key fobs, and the window sticker. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or enthusiast to own a flawless specimen.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
