      "description": "Presented in showroom condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, reflects a standard of care typically reserved for private collections. This is an investment-grade example, offering an uncompromising driving experience for the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection. Meticulously maintained and mechanically beyond reproach, it stands as a definitive benchmark for its class.",
      "price": 44950.0,
